{"tid":1642644,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[國際戰缐] 歐洲巡迴展覧","createTime":"2019-10-09T20:32:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T12:34:49.000Z","uid":73212,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"cc9c5499a3acc8438abd6c8b0a1faca458ebdf50","tid":1642644,"uid":73212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T20:32:51.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">外國勢力 - Free Hong Kong Exhibition團隊</span></span></strong><br />\n上Post : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1592876/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1592876/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\nFree Hong Kong Exhibition團隊由一班海外香港人組成，希望以巡迴展覧形式，將香港人嘅聲音帶到海外。作為响城牆外生活嘅人，我地自覺有責任將港共政府嘅所作所為話俾全世界知。我地或者無能力直接接觸各國政要，但係响西方民主社會，人民就係力量，展覽正正就可以提供一個空間及平台直接與一般市民接觸交流。<br />\n<br />\n响剛剛個weekend (5-7/10)，我地响德國威瑪舉辦咗第二次展覽。威瑪為德國文化重鎮，啱啱一百週年嘅Bauhaus就係响威瑪。响呢個教育程度比較高嘅城市，我地展覽反應唔錯，好多本地人都會主動黎了解今次運動嘅來龍去脈，我地亦會藉此宣揚一下港共嘅所作所為，最意外係其間有一啲內地人黎了解成件事，有啲仲話其實國內有好多人都支持呢個運動，支持嘅人大約五個入面就有一個（唔知真定假啦），只係响大陸無辦法講出口，希望我地作為一個窗口，將內地人嘅聲音由外地傳返入香港，叫香港人加油，打倒中共！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">立場報導:</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/2509663305785941?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F710476795704610%2Fposts%2F2509663305785941%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=FZDcFY5BXo0CBgddFpFX56QEQZ%2FBMmOowG797g%2FgSDo%3D&h=01719bdc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/2509663305785941?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n完成呢次展覽之後，我地繼續Be Water，會將展覽帶去Berlin進行第三站巡迴展，港共越落力，我哋就越起勁幫佢宣揚開去。如果咁啱有朋友响Berlin可以叫佢黎睇下。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">Event page:</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/events/663765374113475/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fevents%2F663765374113475%2F&d=FZDcFY5BXo0CBgddFpFX56QEQZ%2FBMmOowG797g%2FgSDo%3D&h=1dbcb356\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/events/663765374113475/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">我地團隊facebook專頁</span></span></strong>，跟據facebook個algorithm，你地每一個like, follow, share都可以幫我地更容易將訊息傳送出去。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Free-Hong-Kong-Exhibition-110062053719239/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FFree-Hong-Kong-Exhibition-110062053719239%2F&d=FZDcFY5BXo0CBgddFpFX56QEQZ%2FBMmOowG797g%2FgSDo%3D&h=44095ccb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Free-Hong-Kong-Exhibition-110062053719239/</a><br />\n<br />\n我地團隊可以做嘅並唔多，希望大家一齊努力，遍地開花。香港人加油！<br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山，各自努力<br />\n光復香港，時代革命<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cu2DjjM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fcu2DjjM.jpg&h=214a5bf4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xtc4eS9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXtc4eS9.jpg&h=1a4d0bd6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JJLtGyb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJJLtGyb.jpg&h=88d87bae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gaYOGyd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgaYOGyd.jpg&h=ff6ed848&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"121856583dc214559cb3e4c199e3e31716961c0e","tid":1642644,"uid":73212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T20:33:48.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"76da97e72e50bea5545ada7294e64b3cb6a17021","tid":1642644,"uid":73212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T20:34:01.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"6660f2831893b75e232f4d69f7a80b61a9b80686","tid":1642644,"uid":73212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T20:39:49.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"512039f48f1460145ba964352966ee49bf82c2dd","ti